    <item>
      <title>马来西亚公司恳求新税后特朗普关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/malaysian-firms-make-case-against-new-taxes-post-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚制造商敦促政府避免在美国宣布向东南亚国家宣布24％的互惠关税后，今年不再引入额外的税收负担，理由是成本压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/malaysian-firms-make-case-against-new-taxes-post-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 01:35:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本的Ishiba称关税为“国家危机”，因为市场痉挛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/japan-eyes-new-budget-to-help-weather-us-tariff-impact-asahi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本总理史密斯·伊斯皮邦（Shigeru Ishiba）表示，他将与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统举行会议，以解决他所谓的“国家危机”对美国关税的“国家危机”，这导致周五的股票低迷和债券在增长的前景中产生了沉重的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/japan-eyes-new-budget-to-help-weather-us-tariff-impact-asahi</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 00:30:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他认为伊朗将接受直接的核谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-says-he-thinks-iran-is-game-for-direct-nuclear-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，他相信伊朗愿意就其核计划进行直接谈判，这是在德黑兰表示只会通过中介进行谈判的第二天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-says-he-thinks-iran-is-game-for-direct-nuclear-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 21:28:13 GMT</pubDate>
